Package: api.osf.io
Title: Open Science Framework (OSF) API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Open Science Framework API v2.
    Fetch preprints by provider and search public nodes (projects). Uses
    JSON:API format. Includes LLM context injection via osf_context().
